===Etymology===
Derived from {{etyl|la}} ''[[consanguinitas]]'', from ''[[consanguineosus]]'' meaning "consanguineous", from ''[[com-]]'' meaning "together" + ''[[sanguineus]]'' meaning "of or pertaining to blood", from ''[[sanguis]]'' "blood"

